@startuml
!theme toy
autonumber

actor "User (ユーザー)" as User
participant "Grafana (Monitor/全体監視)" as Grafana
participant "ntopng (Microscope/詳細分析)" as Ntop
participant "Devices (Target/調査対象)" as Target

== Phase 1: Detection (異常の検知) ==
User -> Grafana: Check **Throughput** (通信量/bps)
note right: 「全体的に通信量が増えていないか？」を確認
User -> Grafana: Check **Top Talkers** (通信上位者)
note right: 「誰が一番帯域を使っているか？」を特定

== Phase 2: Diagnosis (原因の診断) ==
User -> Ntop: Open ntopng for the specific Device
User -> Ntop: Check **L7 Protocol** (アプリケーションプロトコル)
note right: 「YouTube? BitTorrent? 何のソフトか？」を特定
User -> Ntop: Check **Active Flows** (通信の対話)
note right: 「世界のどこ(IP)と通信しているか？」を特定

== Phase 3: Action (対処) ==
User -> Target: Troubleshoot the Device (デバイスの調査・対処)
@endum